edbackModal_main_5831883\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wgw1705561551164.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wgw1705561551164.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wgw1705561551164.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hxu1665702847192\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Application Shell Triggers\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Almost all application shells share a common set of triggers that can be used to code the behavior of the application or server when it starts.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__p_d12626e1_d12627e1_d12628e1\">The following triggers can be used in all types of application shells:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5942e1_d5943e1_d5944e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jcj1665702550017.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcj1665702550017.html\" title=\"System trigger that starts the application environment and controls the interaction of the application with the component manager.\">trigger apStart</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5945e1_d5946e1_d5947e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__section_r2w_lrh_d1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d280468e77\">Application Shell Triggers</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__p_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1\">Windows and character-based applications provide\n            additional triggers for handling user interactions:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__ul_lh4_prh_d1c\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5948e1_d5949e1_d5950e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xye1665702608643.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xye1665702608643.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request for a menu in a desktop application.\">trigger menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5951e1_d5952e1_d5953e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ppz1665702665163.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ppz1665702665163.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger that defines the application-wide actions in response to the ^SWITCH_KEY action, such as loading a new keyboard translation table.\">trigger keyboardSwitch</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5954e1_d5955e1_d5956e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"niy1665702606431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/niy1665702606431.html\" title=\"Trigger for responding to user-defined key sequences as defined in the Keyboard Translation Table (KTT) or defined in the usys.ini section named as userkeys.\">trigger userKey</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__section_ks5_prh_d1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d280468e128\">Server Shell Triggers</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__p_d12638e1_d12639e1_d12640e1\">Server application shells, the following triggers\n            enable you to define generic behavior before and after activating a component operation\n            in a web environment. Typically, this would include authenticating the user of the web\n            application.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__ul_ehc_srh_d1c\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5957e1_d5958e1_d5959e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uwh1665702683119.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uwh1665702683119.html\" title=\"System trigger for handling any global pre-processing, such as verifying the environment or user permissions.\">trigger preRequest</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hxu1665702847192__li_d5960e1_d5961e1_d5962e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bar1665702683338.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bar1665702683338.html\" title=\"System trigger for handling any global post processing, such as closing a database or writing a log file.\">trigger postRequest</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5831883\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5831883\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Application Shell Triggers Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Application Shell Triggers Almost all application shells share a common set of triggers that can be used to code the behavior of the application or server when it starts. The following triggers can be used in all types of application shells: trigger apStart trigger receiveMessage Application Shell Triggers Windows and character-based applications provide additional triggers for handling user interactions: trigger menu trigger keyboardSwitch trigger userKey Server Shell Triggers Server application shells, the following triggers enable you to define generic behavior before and after activating a component operation in a web environment. Typically, this would include authenticating the user of the web application. trigger preRequest trigger postRequest Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}